<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img src="http://image.blog.livedoor.jp/sonic_channel/imgs/0/4/04fbd231.jpg" width="180" height="240" border="0" alt="080804.jpg" hspace="5" class="pict" align="center"  /><br>
